06_RESEARCH/RESULTS/20260612_carry_feasibility.md:99:No spot history is available in this task, so this is **not** a basis calculation. It only describes mark-price volatility in the 24h window after fixed-threshold extreme funding periods (`|funding| >= 0.10%/8h`).
06_RESEARCH/RESULTS/20260612_carry_feasibility.md:107:Interpretation: the proxy says the periods when funding is most attractive or most punitive often coincide with large mark moves, especially SOL. A formal pre-registration needs actual spot-versus-perp basis data and explicit margin/liquidation rules before any live sizing decision.
