+- `06_RESEARCH/CODE/output/a4_listing_archive_summary.csv`
+- `06_RESEARCH/CODE/output/a4_listing_census_summary.json`
+"""
+    RESULT_PATH.write_text(result_md, encoding="utf-8")
+
+
