+            f"- Per-path target window: `{payload['duration_s']}s`.",
+            "",
+            "## Tool Availability",
+            "",
+            f"- curl: {curl_note}.",
+            f"- websocat: {websocat_note}.",
+            "",
+            "## 判定矩阵",
+            "",
+            "| Path | Client | Proxy | URL | Handshake | Frames | First frame s | Elapsed s | Verdict | Error |",
+            "|---|---|---|---|---:|---:|---:|---:|---|---|",
+            *rows,
+            "",
+            "## Layer Diagnosis",
+            "",
